{"tid":251361,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我係雞","createTime":"2017-05-20T21:33:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-21T01:59:04.000Z","uid":78960,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c9c38327362cac350531335ae2ee84b2cd3b210f","tid":251361,"uid":78960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T21:33:47.000Z","msg":"明知一個男人已經有女朋友<br />\n我仲溝佢係咪好賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢仲要拒絕過我好多次<br />\n我都仲話會等佢<br />\n仲夾硬痴埋去係咪好唔要面？<br />\n明明人地只係當我係雞 玩下就算<br />\n我都仲要中個頭埋去<br />\n仲做埋好多小動作拆散佢地但係都冇用<br />\n<br />\n做錯事嘅人係應該受懲罰<br />\n這世上沒有人可以透過傷害別人獲得幸福"},{"pid":"42b1165c9b888d8e43734e4e9cecfd6e36744ff9","tid":251361,"uid":22952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T21:48:11.000Z","msg":"咪搞鳩我男朋友啦 八婆"},{"pid":"9676e4d56c71ac0d13f30becfee21aacd7a919ac","tid":251361,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T23:17:47.000Z","msg":"你又男朋友又人地男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f5a5acb968e50c3efca0cc07ddd4bc7df2a2084","tid":251361,"uid":35105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T01:33:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">雞就係雞</span></span></span>"},{"pid":"68b1e7c7f130518dd875ea8e40ed1c8c8bd32b0d","tid":251361,"uid":55249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T01:34:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">雞就係雞</span></span></span></blockquote><br />\nagger"},{"pid":"02823fc3c85d1bf458e5245ceab3c682ffd198c0","tid":251361,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T01:35:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">雞就係雞</span></span></span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"d52225